{"tid":2334331,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"人民網：供電可靠性均位居世界前列","createTime":"2020-12-21T06:09:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T18:56:01.000Z","uid":362199,"like":24,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4de9db7ff4a47d6b0be1488a149bcde496ebe425","tid":2334331,"uid":362199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T06:09:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://politics.people.com.cn/BIG5/n1/2019/1119/c429373-31463321.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpolitics.people.com.cn%2FBIG5%2Fn1%2F2019%2F1119%2Fc429373-31463321.html&d=Yr0hxYoWOJ9ZaoTMuy4WzGsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=1c93a313\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://politics.people.com.cn/BIG5/n1/2019/1119/c429373-31463321.html</a><br />\n<br />\n電力是國家基礎工業，事關國計民生、經濟發展。突發的大面積停電事故，將給人民生活和工業生產帶來災難性影響，也會造成供水、交通、通信、金融、商業服務等相關行業和領域的運行癱瘓，給國家安全和社會穩定帶來嚴重威脅。<br />\n<br />\n近些年來，世界上很多國家都發生過大面積停電事故。但在中國，近幾十年不但沒有發生過大面積停電事故，而且經過堅持不斷的發展更新，目前電網安全運行水平、供電可靠性均位居世界前列。<br />\n<br />\n這背后，是中國電力供應保障能力的顯著增強，是中國電網實現了互聯互通互供，是一大批保障電網安全運行技術的成功應用，更是中國特色社會主義制度的體現&hellip;&hellip;它們共同構成了中國沒有發生大面積停電事故的關鍵密碼。"},{"pid":"32d18384fd22fac69d80efa407e0fd6f34c5abd2","tid":2334331,"uid":224561,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T06:11:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cEbr8MK.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcEbr8MK.gif&h=2e5b5c58&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fd26888d0598ae7738c09653336f413fa80c9be3","tid":2334331,"uid":362199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32d18384fd22fac69d80efa407e0fd6f34c5abd2","tid":2334331,"uid":224561,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T06:11:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cEbr8MK.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcEbr8MK.gif&h=2e5b5c58&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T06:14:09.000Z","msg":"繁體？"},{"pid":"785fb35c4aa584c93bfed3e9dd7b71204bceceb4","tid":2334331,"uid":